CinoGear source packaging note

This folder keeps the legacy BotBoarduino_CH3R_PS2 sketch name for Arduino compatibility.
Install the PS2X library from ../PS2X_Library/PS2X_lib into your Arduino libraries folder
before compiling.

Upstream compatibility references:
- SSC-32 / SSC-32U command set
- BotBoarduino-compatible Arduino workflow
- PS2X library by Bill Porter / contributors

See ../docs/THIRD_PARTY_REFERENCES.md and ../docs/COMMERCIAL_RELEASE_NOTES.md
before publishing commercially.
